pskmod

Digital Modulation scheme-Binary Phase Shift Keying Modulation

Calling Sequence

[w,p] = pskmod(Ac,fc,data)

Parameters

fc:carrier signal frequency in Hz
Ac:carrier signal amplitude in volts
data:digital information signal
w:BPSK modulated signal

Description

pskmod -Binary Phase Shift Keying -Digital Phase Modulation of Analog carrier

Examples

fc = 1;//in Hz
Ac = 2; //in volts
data = [1,1,0,0,0,1,1,0];
[w,p] = pskmod(Ac,fc,data);

